    <string name="help_message">Restricted Mode:\nWhen enabled all other apps on the device will be locked until the player gets the required number of problems correct.\n\nStart Free Time:\nStarts reward time instantly.\n\nEnd Reward Time:\nEnds reward time instantly.\n\nGame Type:\nSet the type of problems that will appear. You can mix different types to get a game that contains multiple types of problems. The mistakes setting allows you to play with mistakes from previous games (visible in the History section from the main screen).\n\nGame Length:\nHow long the game will last. Formatted in mm:ss.\n\nCorrect Needed:\nSet how many correct answers are needed to earn reward time.\n\nEarned Time:\nNumber of minutes that will be awarded for a successful game.\n\nDifficulty:\nChange the difficulty of the problems. Harder problems involve larger numbers.</string>
    
